sub_title: English editor & translator for Dutch writers
summary:
No matter the level of English required ~ from easy to esoteric ~ NEEDSer serves  both your own needs as the Dutch client and the needs of your English-reading audience worldwide.
▶ English editing for Dutch writers 
Sensitive correction of your Dutch accent (Dunglish) in your English texts
▶ English translation of Dutch texts 
Sensitive communication of your Dutch meaning in accurate, fluent English
